# Walkthrough: Veroz Generator — Fase 1 Selesai ✅

## Apa yang Telah Dibangun

Seluruh fondasi aplikasi Veroz Generator telah berhasil dibuat dan berjalan di browser.

## Struktur File yang Dibuat

```
Veroz-Generator/
├── package.json          — 30+ dependencies (Next.js, Zustand, Framer Motion, dll)
├── tsconfig.json         — TypeScript config
├── next.config.mjs       — Next.js config (remote image domains)
├── tailwind.config.ts    — Tema futuristik ungu-pink-biru + animasi custom
├── postcss.config.js     — PostCSS
├── .env.local            — Template API keys (isi sebelum deploy)
└── src/
    ├── app/
    │   ├── globals.css       — Tema gelap, glassmorphism, blob animations
    │   ├── layout.tsx        — Root layout + SEO metadata
    │   ├── page.tsx          — Halaman utama (Generator + Gallery + Editor)
    │   └── api/
    │       ├── optimize/route.ts  — Gemini / Groq / Fallback prompt optimizer
    │       └── generate/route.ts  — Pollinations.ai / HuggingFace image gen
    ├── components/
    │   ├── Navbar.tsx          — Tab navigator + Quota bar + Login button
    │   ├── StyleSelector.tsx   — Grid 12 gaya stiker
    │   ├── PromptArea.tsx      — Textarea + Suggestion pills + Bantuan AI + Ide Acak
    │   ├── StickerTextInput.tsx — Nama, teks, emoji picker, font, posisi teks
    │   ├── ReferenceUpload.tsx — Drag-drop upload + mode (Full/Wajah/Badan)
    │   ├── BackgroundToggle.tsx — Toggle transparan + color picker + preset warna
    │   ├── GenerateControls.tsx — Rasio sosmed + AI model + Generate button + Quota
    │   ├── PreviewGrid.tsx     — Grid adaptif preview + hover (Re-generate, Unduh, Simpan)
    │   └── Gallery.tsx         — Koleksi stiker + Sticker Packs + ZIP download
    ├── lib/
    │   ├── utils.ts      — Helper functions + 15+ rasio sosmed
    │   ├── types.ts      — TypeScript types (Sticker, Pack, Form, User, dll)
    │   └── supabase.ts   — Supabase client factory
    └── store/
        └── useStore.ts   — Zustand store (form, results, stickers, packs, user)
```

